a sorted order on each addition or deletion of Lesson objects, whereas
HashSet does not.

commitResults.messageBody:
Previously, lessons with a broad time range such that existing lessons time ranges
are completely contained in the time range can be added. Failure to detect clash and throw
error.

Time range validation now checks if either the newly added lesson's range contains existing lessons'
time ranges, vice versa.
